<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>Arul Blog</title><link href="http://www.arulraj.net/" rel="alternate"></link><link href="http://www.arulraj.net/feeds/tag/recent-post.atom.xml" rel="self"></link><id>http://www.arulraj.net/</id><updated>2009-03-04T09:47:00+05:30</updated><entry><title>Recent Post Widget in Flash</title><link href="http://www.arulraj.net/2009/03/recent-post-widget-in-flash.html" rel="alternate"></link><published>2009-03-04T09:47:00+05:30</published><author><name>arul</name></author><id>tag:www.arulraj.net,2009-03-04:2009/03/recent-post-widget-in-flash.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;The widget is shows like that... This is the Beta version only.. Unfortunately it supports only for feed burner feed... I will update this soon...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference external" href="http://sharedaa.com/images/Arul/RssReader.swf?feedUrl=http://feeds2.feedburner.com/blogspot/TLLQ?format=xml&amp;amp;feedItems=12&amp;amp;bgcolor=D8D7CC&amp;amp;border=BDBCB6&amp;amp;title=Recent+Books"&gt;See this Link&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;How to use... Use the Below script...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;center&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;embed&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;pluginspage&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;http://www.macromedia.com/go/getflashplayer&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;quality&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;high&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;align&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;flashvars&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;application/x-shockwave-flash&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;height&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;400&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;src&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;http://sharedaa.com/images/Arul/RssReader.swf?feedUrl=http://feeds2.feedburner.com/blogspot/TLLQ?format=xml&amp;amp;feedItems=12&amp;amp;bgcolor=D8D7CC&amp;amp;border=BDBCB6&amp;amp;title=Recent+Books&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;bgcolor&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;#FFFFFF&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;width&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;500&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;RssReader&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;embed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;center&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Variabels&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;feedUrl - URL of the Feed&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;feedItems - No of feed you want to display&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;bgcolor - Background color of the widget&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;border - Border and Header color of the widget&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;title - Header name of the widget&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here the &lt;a class="reference external" href="http://booksforpeople.blogspot.com"&gt;http://booksforpeople.blogspot.com&lt;/a&gt; feed is used&lt;/p&gt;
